  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DobbyxEscape: Halloween Adventure</h2></strong><br>It is All Hallow's Eve and there's a magical party to attend!<br><br>When you arrive there, however, your witch friend needs your help!<br><br>Her party potion is far from ready and she needs the essence from five mystic locations!<br><br>It's up to you to help her out before time runs out and the party is a disaster!<br><br>Are you up for the challenge?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183380/extras/a1b3668fcec198107d90de29e913aa6f.poster.avif?t=1667059707\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183380/extras/a1b3668fcec198107d90de29e913aa6f.webm?t=1667059707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183380/extras/a1b3668fcec198107d90de29e913aa6f.mp4?t=1667059707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Room Escape game!<br></li><li>Six locations to discover!<br></li><li>Beautiful graphics bring the game to life!<br></li><li>Many items to collect and puzzles to solve!<br></li><li>Fun soundtrack and sound effects!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183380/extras/209ee3c41e36a9b2db3359f37276eb4f.poster.avif?t=1667059707\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183380/extras/209ee3c41e36a9b2db3359f37276eb4f.webm?t=1667059707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2183380/extras/209ee3c41e36a9b2db3359f37276eb4f.mp4?t=1667059707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
